Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的 高盧
