Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的蟲豸們
