Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜 我們也趕快前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
